item.description:
@Hyperon wrote:

I recommend using an IDE, and stopping the camera from moving about. It’s hard to see. This will improve your quality of videos.

Make tutorials on how to create methods and variables and how they can be used in RSPS. Make tutorials on how to debug. Make tutorials on how to add additions to player saving and loading. Things like that.

Editing text isn’t a tutorial.
